  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Manager (Retail Operations & Trade Marketing)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Apparel/ Retail industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Sales Manager (Retail Operations & Trade Marketing) </strong>to join their dynamic team: </p><ul><li><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Permanent</li><li><strong>Position:</strong> Sales Manager</li><li><strong>Location:</strong> Central (Nearest MRT: Rochor) </li><li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, Office Hours</li><li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $5,000 + AWS </li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities: </strong></p><ul><li>Curate and propose attractive products for in-store events and promotions.</li><li>Research and recommend new business opportunities to drive sales and service improvements.</li><li>Maintain service and operational standards with the sales team.</li><li>Conduct product training and mentor retail staff.</li><li>Ensure compliance with company policies, SOPs, and POP/product display requirements.</li><li>Build and maintain relationships with internal and external stakeholders.</li><li>Monitor inventory levels, assist with stock movements, and support event setups.</li><li>Prepare weekly and monthly reports for management.</li><li>Support daily retail operations, logistics, and ad-hoc tasks as needed.</li><li>Collaborate with the sales team to develop strategies and achieve targets.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>At least a Diploma with minimum 3 years of related experience as a Sales Manager in the Retail Industry.</li><li>Proficient with MS Office (Especially Excel and PowerPoint), Adobe Photoshop or Adobe Illustrator will be added advantage.</li><li>Willing to work on weekends and Public Holidays when there are events or whenever required.</li></ul><p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong> </p><ul><li>Click the APPLY button, or </li><li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to<strong> </strong><a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com.</strong></a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing. </li></ul><p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em><em> </em><br /></p><p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA). <br /></p><p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641 </p><p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
